					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Brad Bigelow</h4>
												<p>Brad Bigelow is a writer, instructor, and editor living in Missoula, Montana. He is the editor of the Recovered Books series for Boiler House Press and has been a writer for the Neglected Books website since 2006. With more than six hundred articles, the site celebrates the work of little-known writers.</p>
